<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>infra-as-code-lab</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: monospace; background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 2rem 3rem; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center; }
    h1 { color: #58a6ff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p  { color: #8b949e; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
    .tag { background: #21262d; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>infra-as-code-lab</h1>
    <p>Provisioned by <span class="tag">Terraform</span> - Configured by <span class="tag">Ansible</span></p>
    <p>Host: <strong>{{ ansible_hostname }}</strong></p>
    <p>Environment: <strong>{{ app_server_name }}</strong></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
